      "side": 1,
      "message": "There are a couple of places where the falcon behavior makes sense, for example on dimension arguments for a measurement-list:\n\nmeasurement-list?dimension\u003dservice:monitoring\u0026dimension\u003dhostname:mini-mon\n\nInstead we make them specify it this way:\n\nmeasurement-list?dimension\u003dservice:monitoring,hostname:mini-mon\n\nThe Falcon behavior implies that a significant number of people believe the first is a legitimate form",
      "revId": "6f924db98dc44d19370fcd1c77c9ab1df9e1f10a",
      "serverId": "4a232e18-c5a9-48ee-94c0-e04e7cca6543",
